snippet: Police say they arrested a burglar at the Los Angeles home of Sandra Bullock while the actress was there, but she wasn't harmed....

headline.print_headline: Police: Burglar Arrested at Sandra Bullock's Home
headline.main: Police: Burglar Arrested at Sandra Bullock's Home

lead_paragraph: Police say they arrested a burglar at the Los Angeles home of Sandra Bullock while the actress was there, but she wasn't harmed.
